=== Xbox One X ===
[[File:XBOX_ONE_X_Gamescom_(36042607743).jpg|thumb]]
Xbox One X 開發代號“天蝎座计划”(Project Scorpio)，最早在2016年6月14日的E3发布会上宣布。此主机拥有6TFLOPs的单精度浮点性能，浮点性能将是Xbox One的4.6倍，索尼PS4的3.26倍，该主机在2017年11月7日上市。Digital Foundry 受邀參加xbox技術預覽後釋出更為詳細的主機規格：2.3GHz訂製8核心CPU、GPU為訂製的AMD Polaris核心，內含40個計算單元(compute units)，時脈為1172Mhz。記憶體為12GB GDDR5，[[内存带宽|記憶體頻寬]]326GB/s，其中3GB做為系統保留，遊戲可用記憶體為9GB。<ref>[http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/06/08/xbox-scorpio-extra-gigabyte-of-ram-unlocked-for-developers Xbox Scorpio: Extra Gigabyte of RAM Unlocked for Developers] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/06/08/xbox-scorpio-extra-gigabyte-of-ram-unlocked-for-developers |date=20220418212202 }}.</ref>Xbox One X為了最佳化Direct3D 12還另外增加了指令處理器(Command Processor)專門處理一些較高頻率的API呼叫，例如繪圖呼叫指令(Draw calls)，如此得以大幅降低繪圖時CPU的使用率。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/digitalfoundry-2017-project-scorpio-tech-revealed |title=Inside the next Xbox: Project Scorpio tech revealed |access-date=2017-04-19 |archive-date=2017-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170504225818/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/digitalfoundry-2017-project-scorpio-tech-revealed }}</ref>主机散热方面采用了液體冷卻均熱板散熱技術。<ref>[https://www.theverge.com/2017/6/11/15774918/microsoft-xbox-one-x-release-date-price-new-console-announced-e3-2017 Xbox One X is Microsoft's next game console, arriving on November 7th for $499] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theverge.com/2017/6/11/15774918/microsoft-xbox-one-x-release-date-price-new-console-announced-e3-2017 |date=20170612004033 }}.TheVerge.2017-06-11.[2017-06-12].</ref>

2020年7月16日，微软确认Xbox One X将停产。<ref name="XOX & XSD end">[https://www.theverge.com/2020/7/16/21327330/microsoft-xbox-one-x-s-digital-edition-discontinued Microsoft discontinues Xbox One X and Xbox One S digital edition ahead of Series X launch] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/7/16/21327330/microsoft-xbox-one-x-s-digital-edition-discontinued |date=20200717071905 }}.TheVerge.2020-07-16.[2020-07-18].</ref>

